<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <style>
      /* common style  */
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Baskerville:wght@400;700&display=swap");
      body {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0px 10px 0px 20px;
      }
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .page {
        text-align: justify;
        font-family: "Libre Baskerville", serif;
        width: 210mm;
        margin: 0px auto;
        background-image: url("<%= baseUrl %>/uploads/ollato-images/regular-page-bg.svg");
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
      }
      .sub-page {
        padding: 50px 20px 0px;
        min-height: calc(29.7cm - 70px);
      }
      footer {
        width: 210mm;
        margin: 0px auto;
      }
      @page {
        size: A4;
        margin: 0;
      }
      @media print {
        html, body {
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;        
        }
        .page {
          margin: 0;
          width: initial;
          min-height: initial;
          page-break-after: always;
        }
      }
      .sub-page img {
        width: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 24px;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .page-content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .fist-letter-big {
        color: black;
        font-size: 19px;
      }
      .color-latter {
        color: #0f62ac;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      /* sub page  */
      .qoutes-heading {
        padding-top: 10px;
        border-top: 2px solid #0f62ac;
        max-width: 70%;
        margin: 0px auto 0px;
      }
      .header-content {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .welcome-summery {
        margin-top: 100px;
      }
      /* footer  */
      .footer-content {
        display: flex;
        position: relative;
        justify-content: space-between;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .footer-content p,
      a {
        padding-bottom: 0px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      }
      footer p,
      a {
        font-size: 11px;
        line-height: 18px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="page">
        <div class="sub-page">
          <header>
            <div class="header-content">
              <h1 style="padding-bottom: 30px">Welcome To Ollato</h1>
              <div class="qoutes-heading">
                <p style="font-weight: 600">
                  " If four things are followed-having a great aim, acquiring
                  knowledge, hard work, and preserverance-then anything can be
                  achieved"
                </p>
                <p style="font-style: italic; font-weight: 600" class="name">
                  -A. P. J. Abdul Kalam
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </header>
          <div class="welcome-summery">
            <p class="dear-name">
              Dear <%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %>,
            </p>
            <p>Welcome to the world of career possibilities!</p>
            <p>
              Congratulations on successfully completing “Ollato Comprehensive
              Career Assessment” pertaining to your Interest and Aptitude. The
              findings are here. A detailed self-explanatory career guidance
              report has been generated by an expert panel at Ollato, to
              identify the most suited career options for you to explore.
            </p>
            <p>In case of any doubts feel free to contact us.</p>
            <p>
              We look forward to being associated with you on this journey of
              career discovery.
            </p>
            <p>All the Best!</p>
            <p>With Best Regards,</p>
            <p>Team Ollato</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="padding-bottom: 10px">
          <footer style="background-color: #0f62ac">
            <section>
              <div class="footer-content">
                <div>
                  <p style="text-transform: uppercase" class="footer-name">
                    <b><%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %></b>
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="center-footer">
                  <p>
                    618, Nirmal Corporate Centre, LBS Road, Moti Nagar, Mulund West, Mumbai – 400080,
                  </p>
                  <p>Maharashtra (INDIA) <a href="tel:02235130089">TEL: (022) 35130089 & +91 9967153285</a></p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p>02</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
